1. *Moj* pas voli da trči u parku. (My dog loves to run in the park.)
2. Volim da gledam *moje* omiljene filmove vikendom. (I love to watch my favorite movies on the weekends.)
3. *Moja* majka je veoma brižna prema meni. (My mother is very caring towards me.)
4. *Mojim* prijateljima se sviđa nova restoranska ponuda. (My friends like the new restaurant menu.)
5. Često slušam *moju* omiljenu pesmu kad se osećam loše. (I often listen to my favorite song when I feel bad.)
6. *Moja* sestra studira psihologiju na fakultetu. (My sister is studying psychology at the university.)
7. Učiteljica je pohvalila *moj* sastav pred celim razredom. (The teacher praised my essay in front of the whole class.)
8. *Moje* dete je već veliko i ne zavisi više toliko od mene. (My child is already big and doesn't depend on me that much anymore.)
9. Kada sam otišao u inostranstvo, jako mi je nedostajala *moja* porodica. (When I went abroad, I missed my family a lot.)
10. *Moje* omiljene boje su plava i zelena. (My favorite colors are blue and green.)